<plot>A farmer's daughter falls in love with an artist, who wants to paint her. She rejects her other suitor, a farmhand who works for her father, and agrees t let the artist paint her. However, the artist isn't exactly who she thinks he is, and when she has a life-threatening accident, she finds out who it is who really loves her.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?240797</url></doc>
